# Environment Variables

## Supabase Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

## IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# - NEVER use SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY in client-side code
# - The anon key is safe to expose as it respects Row Level Security (RLS)
# - Service role key should ONLY be used in server-side API routes if needed
# - Always enable Row Level Security policies on your Supabase tables

## Optional: For server-side operations only
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key_for_server_only
